{"tid":1033604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擦唔切鞋 民建聯的人大代表提交的提案包括，在中山、珠海等地，興建只供香港人居住的房屋","createTime":"2019-02-23T09:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T08:06:00.000Z","uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5704f1f1d4ea4eac3381d5750e48b0489037001f","tid":1033604,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】兩會下月北京召開，民建聯提交24項提案或建議。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民建聯的人大代表提交的提案包括，在中山、珠海等地，興建只供香港人居住的房屋，而豁免住戶跟從內地稅制，又建議簡化內地過關手續，例如在皇崗口岸實施一地兩檢。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而針對日前推出的粵港澳大灣區發展規劃綱要，民建聯建議建立統一的大灣區資訊平台及創業配對平台，為打算在大灣區內居住、創業的市民提供資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=338468&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338468%26refer%3D&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1HhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=3f161428\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338468%26refer%3D&h=32448b2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=338468&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n有權就可以仆街到咁"},{"pid":"29839df3294c30ef375d696b2764678aa8ed6c69","tid":1033604,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ed3e376b7fbcaf2901876fa7d9c9850ef7fd8a","tid":1033604,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"接受現實啦香港人"},{"pid":"0ccbcff2edfa49b4bffbf8afc57ecb4c47172c22","tid":1033604,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33909860c0563cd1c7ac367723248bcddace88d9","tid":1033604,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":